<font size="+3"; color="blue">aim_ranweps_v2</font>

The map spawns a random weapon each round, with a deagle and knife. The 

purpose of random weapons is for training your aim with most important 

weapons :)
<fieldset><legend>Random Weapons</legend>sg552
ak47
m4a1
awp
scout
famas
galil
ump45
mp5navy
p90
</fieldset>I have edited the vmt files of some textures (the boxes) and changed them into wood material.

<font size="+">I have minimized the boxes size and removed the dark parts from the v1.</font>

<font size="+2"; color="green">If you liked the map rate it!!</font>
